title: Kosmas Epsilon - One Hour Trance Party Mix (by Dj Henriko)
description:
Here is another mix that I made today, I got inspired by the first 
	song on "Tiesto - Live @ Amnesia Ibiza (Essential Mix) - 08-07-2005"
	(highly recommended to download btw)

	The songs that I mixed together was songs by Kosmas Epsilon. Two
	of the songs are actually just remixed by him as you can see in the
	list below.

	Hope you will enjoy!

	/ Dj Henriko
